 *
 * Returns associative list of strings. Best practice is to append information to existing entries with `+=`, if present (This is null safe), i.e.:
 * ```dm
 * . = ..()
 * .["Screwdriver"] += "<p>Toggles the maintenance panel open and closed.</p>"
 * ```
 */
